otherFacts.name: Interior Features
otherFacts.value: Attic Stairs Pulldown, Kitchen Island, Garden Tub

data.description: New Year! New Home! 4 bedroom open floor-plan.  Gourmet kitchen with double oven, electric cook top island and walk in pantry. Spacious dining room with cofferred ceiling. 2 story family room with wood-burning FP.  Bedroom and full bath down.  Beautiful master suite upstairs tiled master bath with garden tub, granite counter tops.  Catwalk over looks 2-story family room with lots of windows and wood burning FP.  Must see.
